10:38:59.000Z","msg":"有人格障礙了，畀啲空間佢啦<br />\n我信佢老母操控佢呀，不過佢自己又無膽搬出去自己生活。<br />\n<br />\n講真，一搬出去住，住個三百幾呎細單位，條女實現形"},{"pid":"70589101b0d308e3e6216ca35c58ce9334508228","tid":2288199,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:39:55.000Z","msg":"林作想用花邊新聞炒熱自己姐，唔理距咪得"},{"pid":"b46b0427fe8440205241c972a2aa435a128b351f","tid":2288199,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:41:13.000Z","msg":"林x (裙腳仔)"},{"pid":"3cd57bd32a521e88a43798ffabdbc48db77298f5","tid":2288199,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T12:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a07b8d662f3e1f8bfff1ee0005639d78e18b2aa","tid":2288199,"uid":300782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T12:20:02.000Z","msg":"你屌你自己老母關人差事"},{"pid":"4644ad36455a3ccbdb6ec2d221c85ada4ee06c88","tid":2288199,"uid":70800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T12:20:58.000Z","msg":"Wfc"},{"pid":"e247cd0aab6092ec1ccbd39c4d186989924c2c06","tid":2288199,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T12:20:59.000Z","msg":"呢鋪今次真係 吔咩爹 吔咩嗲 搭錯車<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}